ACS Sees Two-Part Sale of Renewable-Energy Assets in 2011, Cinco Reports

-- B y   T o d d   W h i t e
-- 
2011-04-15T07:17:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-15/acs-sees-two-part-sale-of-renewable-energy-assets-in-2011-cinco-reports.html
Actividades de Construccion y
Servicios SA’s planned sale of its renewable-energy plants may
take place in two parts, with 349 megawatts of solar-thermal
installations offered in the first round, Cinco Dias reported.  That may be followed by selling 1,799 megawatts of wind
farms in  Spain , Portugal, Mexico, Peru and Brasil, the newspaper
reported, citing comments by the Madrid-based company’s
executives yesterday at the annual meeting. The construction
company expects to sell almost the entire portfolio this year,
the report said.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
